/*
    Will save or the target monster is Dominated for
    3 turns +1 per caster level.
*/
//:://////////////////////////////////////////////
//:: Created By: Preston Watamaniuk
//:: Created On: Jan 29, 2001
//:://////////////////////////////////////////////
